          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FOUR",
        "comment": "Mixed comment/no-comment test: car came back sparkling. Confirmed mixed works.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-04T12:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-04T12:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev006",
        "reviewId": "rev006",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Lucy Santana",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev006",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "My 2019 Tesla Model 3 looks brand new after the ceramic coating package. They even cleaned the charge port! Price was very fair. Will be a repeat customer.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-06T11:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-06T11:00:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Lucy, ceramic coating on Teslas is one of our specialties! Thanks for the detailed review. See you for the 6-month follow-up! 🚗",
          "updateTime": "2026-04-06T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev008",
        "reviewId": "rev008",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Nina Patel",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev008",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "Booked the interior deep clean after moving cross-country. Pet hair, sand, everything — gone. They spent 4 hours and I couldn't believe the transformation. Worth every cent.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-08T14:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-08T14:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev010",
        "reviewId": "rev010",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Oscar Reid",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev010",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "TWO",
        "comment": "The outside was cleaned well but they missed a big stain on the back seat that I specifically highlighted on the intake form. Had to point it out after. They fixed it but I shouldn't have had to ask.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-10T13:30:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-10T13:30:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Oscar, that's on us — the intake form should be the checklist we check off, not a secondary afterthought. Thank you for flagging it. We've updated our process.",
          "updateTime": "2026-04-10T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev012",
        "reviewId": "rev012",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Paula Evans",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev012",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FOUR",
        "comment": "Prompt service, friendly staff, car returned on time. The tire dressing was a nice extra touch that wasn't even on the package I bought.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-12T15:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-12T15:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev013",
        "reviewId": "rev013",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Rob Matthews",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev013",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "Third time using them. Loyalty discount program is a nice touch. The quality is consistent every single visit which is rare in detailing. My F-150 looks show-ready.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-14T10:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-14T10:00:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Rob, three visits and counting — thank you for your loyalty! Your F-150 deserves VIP treatment and we'll keep delivering. 🏆",
          "updateTime": "2026-04-14T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev014",
        "reviewId": "rev014",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Sara Kim",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev014",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "THREE",
        "comment": "Good job on the exterior. Interior was rushed — dust still visible on the dashboard vents. For the premium package price, I expected more attention to detail (literally).",
        "createTime": "2026-04-16T11:30:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-16T11:30:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Sara, 'attention to detail' is literally our business — you're right to call this out. We've added a vent-cleaning checklist to all premium packages.",
          "updateTime": "2026-04-16T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev015",
        "reviewId": "rev015",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Tim Nguyen",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev015",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "Best detailer in Portland. I've tried 4 others. Nobody comes close for paint correction work. My 15-year-old Honda looks like it rolled off the showroom floor.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-18T09:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-18T09:00:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Tim, that's high praise considering you've tested the competition! Paint correction is our craft and we'll keep earning that trust. 🎨",
          "updateTime": "2026-04-18T23:59:00Z"
        }
      }
